PESHAWAR Feb 07 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi and Caretaker Chief Minister of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa (KPK) Muhammad Azam Khan on Tuesday discussed the law and order and overall situation in the province.
They held a meeting at the CM house, President Secretariat Press Wing said in a press release.
